{"tid":1614112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[風向]如何教育左膠","createTime":"2019-10-02T16:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T18:30:02.000Z","uid":163747,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"87e3c3361e719b462f8bd7d7d039652e4aca1803","tid":1614112,"uid":163747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:49:50.000Z","msg":"「唔好搞店/鐵/商場，要<strong>對準政權</strong>」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />回應：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">佢哋係政權喺經濟層面嘅延伸，打擊佢哋等同打撃政權</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n「與怪物戰鬥的人，要小心自己<strong>不要變成怪物</strong>；當你望向深淵，深淵也同時在凝視著你」<br />\n怪物定義：(1)失去理性、(2)敵視周遭非我族裔的物體，並構成具體威脅。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />回應：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">示威者有理性有目標地行動，只針對個別目標，而不是無差別攻擊，決不攻擊無辜人士</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n「但我懇請你們不要<strong>被仇恨支配自己</strong>，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />回應：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">示威者的行動不只是報復，更是打擊政權。有特定的行動與目標反映示威行動經過思考</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nBTW <span style=\"color: red;\">論述=風向</span> 我哋一齊帶返個好風向出嚟好嘛 <br />\n一齊集思廣益應付對家想帶嘅風向啦喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034456f8db677acdf84a92612b52fe72e7d14501","tid":1614112,"uid":163747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:50:43.000Z","msg":"如果覺得有道理可唔可以幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2602c4a16bc1f826e701a804ec36a72d32442f09","tid":1614112,"uid":163747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:51:44.000Z","msg":"留下言幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該大家"},{"pid":"c240dd0473042e9f58e02b7daa211d02f08d9c6e","tid":1614112,"uid":163747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:52:51.000Z","msg":"又或者有冇論述未知點回應 都可以打上嚟 一齊諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d33e272c15fe82745